Commands :-)

1. cordova create cordova tt.net.boardz BoardZ

2. cordova platform add ios android windows --save

3. cordova plugin add cordova-plugin-whitelist cordova-plugin-statusbar cordova-plugin-splashscreen cordova-plugin-geolocation cordova-plugin-camera cordova-plugin-crosswalk-webview --save




